(8,	'Food and Beverages',	'Food and Beverages',	'foodIcon.png',	'food-and-beverages',	1,	'Food and Beverages Industry Analysis and Market Research Reports',	'The Food and Beverages Industry is the chief revenue generator over the globe. It has been witnessing diverse patterns from organic food items to beverages; the on-going demand is ascribed to the search for more beneficial choices. The demand for food might be endless yet is controlled by eminent trends.',	'2018-03-13 14:36:59'),
