(10,	'Machinery and Equipments',	'Machinery and Equipments',	'machIcon.png',	'machinery-and-equipments',	1,	'Machinery and Equipments Industry Analysis and Market Research Reports',	'Machinery is characterized as any gadget or machine device part that accomplishes work leveraging mechanical or electrical energy. We help customers ranging from SMEs to niche players and commodity producers to find the solutions that matter through the entire value chain from mining through distribution. ',	'2018-03-13 14:37:33'),
(11,	'Materials and Chemicals',	'Materials and Chemicals',	'chemIcon.png',	'materials-and-chemicals',	1,	'Materials and Chemicals Industry Analysis and Market Research Reports',	'Materials and Chemicals market research is an essential fragment of what forms business today since chemicals and materials are one of the quickest developing sectors. There have been enormous and breakthrough innovations and developments in the recent past, which are canvassed in the research.',	'2018-03-13 14:37:50'),
(12,	'Medical Devices',	'Medical Devices',	'mediIcon.png',	'medical-devices',	1,	'Medical Devices Industry Analysis and Market Research Reports',	'The blend of IT with medical devices is changing the scenario of patient care. Medicinal devices integrated with mobile applications for monitoring and diagnosis of disease conditions eliminates the cost of diagnosis. Likewise, assessing health measures is no longer restricted to in-clinic visit.',	'2018-03-13 14:38:07'),
(13,	'Pharmaceuticals and Healthcare',	'Pharmaceuticals and Healthcare',	'healthIcon.png',	'pharmaceuticals-and-healthcare',	1,	'Pharmaceuticals and Healthcare Industry Analysis and Market Research Reports',	'The healthcare industry in the last decade has seen phenomenal development attributable to enhanced and innovative technologies and the development of cutting-edge infrastructural facilities. Faster regulatory approvals and steady R&D activities have positively affected the pharmaceutical industry.',	'2018-03-13 14:38:25'),
(14,	'Semiconductor and Electronics',	'Semiconductor and Electronics',	'electricIcon.png',	'semiconductor-and-electronics',	1,	'Semiconductor and Electronics Industry Analysis and Market Research Reports',	'The Semiconductor and Electronics industry is a relatively competitive market across the globe that requires massive capital investments. With the ever-increasing competition, there is an increased effort to bring about the innovation of better-evaluated products, which would render more successful administrations.',	'2018-03-13 14:38:50'),
