quo; immune system which hampers the growth of the sugar-based excipients market. However, factors that restrain the market are the shortage of FDA approval due to the rigorous regulatory requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Business Intelligence:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the American Pharmaceutical Review, around 35 products have been launched by using Zydis ODT technology in 60 countries worldwide in 2016. Sugar alcohol differs in sweetness level and calorie content. Sweetness level of this sugar-based excipient range from 50-100% to that of sugar. According to the Food and Drug Administration (FDA), Indian firms have received 40% of new U.S. approvals for the generic drugs in the recent years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Regional Analysis:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on the regional analysis, the global market is segmented into North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, and LAMEA. Due to investment in the production and drug development of the generic drugs, as well various government policies, Western and Eastern Europe is expected to command a significant market share of the global market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key players:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Cargill, Inc.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Ashland Inc.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Archer Daniels Midland Company</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Roquette Group</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>The Lubrizol Corporation</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Meggle AG</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>BASF SE</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Colorcon Inc.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Among Others</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The report will provide-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Impact of COVID-19 on Demand and Supply</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>How the market will recover in upcoming years</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Market Sizing and Forecast for segments and sub-segments</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Market Factor